{"id":270,"ayahs":[{"number":27,"arabic":"ثُمَّ يَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ يُخْزِيهِمْ وَيَقُولُ أَيْنَ شُرَكَآءِىَ ٱلَّذِينَ كُنتُمْ تُشَٰٓقُّونَ فِيهِمْ ۚ قَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُوا۟ ٱلْعِلْمَ إِنَّ ٱلْخِزْىَ ٱلْيَوْمَ وَٱلسُّوٓءَ عَلَى ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ","translation":"And then, on Resurrection Day, He will cover them [all] with ignominy, and will say: \"Where, now, are those beings to whom you ascribed a share in My divinity, [and] for whose sake you cut yourselves off [from My guidance]?\" [Whereupon] those who [in their lifetime] were endowed with knowledge will say: \"Verily, ignominy and misery [have fallen] this day upon those who have been denying the truth-","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1928.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":30389,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"অতঃপর","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30390,"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"দিনে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30391,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ","translation":"ক্বিয়ামাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30392,"position":4,"arabic":"يُخْزِيهِمْ","translation":"তিনি লাঞ্ছিত করবেন তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30393,"position":5,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُ","translation":"এবং বলবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30394,"position":6,"arabic":"أَيْنَ","translation":"\"কোথায়","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30395,"position":7,"arabic":"شُرَكَآءِىَ","translation":"আমার শরীকরা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30396,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যাদের (ব্যাপারে)","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30397,"position":9,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_027_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30398,"position":10,"arabic":"تُشَـٰٓقُّونَ","translation":"তর্কাতর্