 do any evil! [But they will be answered:] \"Yea, verily, God has full knowledge of all that you were doing!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1929.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":31402,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যাদের (অবস্থান হলো এই)","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31403,"position":2,"arabic":"تَتَوَفَّىٰهُمُ","translation":"তাদের মৃত্যু ঘটায়","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31404,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ","translation":"ফেরেশতারা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31405,"position":4,"arabic":"ظَالِمِىٓ","translation":"অত্যাচারী অবস্থায়","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31406,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنفُسِهِمْ ۖ","translation":"নিজেদের উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31408,"position":6,"arabic":"فَأَلْقَوُا۟","translation":"তারা যখন আত্নসমর্পন করবে (এবং বলবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31409,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلسَّلَمَ","translation":"শান্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31410,"position":8,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"\"না","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31411,"position":9,"arabic":"كُنَّا","translation":"আমরা ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31412,"position":10,"arabic":"نَعْمَلُ","translation":"আমরা কাজ করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31413,"position":11,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31414,"position":12,"arabic":"سُوٓءٍۭ ۚ","translation":"মন্দ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31416,"position":13,"arabic":"بَلَىٰٓ","translation":"হ্যাঁ","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31417,"position":14,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31418,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31419,"position":16,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۢ","translation":"খুব জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31420,"position":17,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ সম্পর্কে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31421,"position":18,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31422,"position":19,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা কাজ করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_028_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31423,"position":20,"arabic":"٢٨","translation":"(২৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":29,"arabic":"فَٱدْخُلُوٓا۟ أَبْوَٰبَ جَهَنَّمَ خَٰلِدِينَ فِيهَا ۖ فَلَبِئْسَ مَثْوَى ٱلْمُتَكَبِّرِينَ","translation":"Hence, enter the gates of hell, therein to abide!\" And evil, indeed, shall be the state of all who are given to false pride!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1930.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":32386,"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱدْخُلُوٓا۟","translation":"সুতরাং তোমরা প্রবেশ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32387,"position":2,"arabic":"أَبْوَٰبَ","translation":"দরজাসমূহে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32388,"position":3,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","translation":"জাহান্নামের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32389,"position":4,"arabic":"خَـٰلِدِينَ","translation":"স্থায়ী বসবাসকারী হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32390,"position":5,"arabic":"فِيهَا ۖ","translation":"তার মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32392,"position":6,"arabic":"فَلَبِئْسَ","translation":"অতএব অবশ্যই নিকৃষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32393,"position":7,"arabic":"مَثْوَى","translation":"আবাসস্থল","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32394,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَكَبِّرِينَ","translation":"অহংকারীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_029_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32395,"position":9,"arabic":"٢٩","translation":"(২৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":30,"arabic":"۞ وَقِيلَ لِلَّذِينَ ٱتَّقَوْا۟ مَاذَآ أَنزَلَ رَبُّكُمْ ۚ قَالُوا۟ خَيْرًۭا ۗ لِّلَّذِينَ أَحْسَنُوا۟ فِى هَٰذِهِ ٱلدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةٌۭ ۚ وَلَدَارُ ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ خَيْرٌۭ ۚ وَلَنِعْمَ دَارُ ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ","translation":"But [when] those who are conscious of God are asked, \"What is it that your Sustainer has bestowed from on high?\" -they answer, \"Goodness supreme!\" Good fortune awaits, in this world, all who persevere in doing good; but their ultimate state will be far better still: for, how excellent indeed will be the state of the God-conscious [in the life to come]!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1931.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":33216,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَقِيلَ","translation":"এবং বলা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_030_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33217,"position":2,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা (তাদেরকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/016_030_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33218,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱتَّقَوْا۟","translation":"তাকওয়া অবলম্বন করতো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_030_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33219,"position":4,"arabic":"مَاذَآ","translation":"\"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/016_030_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33220,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছিলেন\"","audioUrl":"wbw/016_030_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33221,"position":6,"arabic":"رَبُّكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের রব\"","audioUrl":"wbw/016_030_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33223,"position":7,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_030_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33224,"position":8,"arabic":"خَيْرًۭا ۗ","translation":